snippet.title: Cat designer Mocha Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cat Designer Mocha - english version is coming to iOS and Android in 2022!*
*The scheduled release date will change to 2022. 

"I'm gonna become a designer in this town!" Mocha is a cat, and her dream journey starts here.  In this game you need to complete puzzles of matching to explore her story. 

- Puzzle: Look at the picture, and find the correct place for each item. When you find it, place the item exactly on same on the picture. Once you place the item, a cute animal guest will arrive.Enjoy create a collection album.

Cat Designer Mocha is the newest game from Kotoriyama.

Kotoriyama Website: ​https://kotoriyama.com/mocha/
Kotoriyama  Twitter: https://twitter.com/kotoriyama_
